<p class="western" lang="en-US" align="center"><span style="font-size: large;"><strong>Free website terms and conditions: drafting notes</strong></span></p>
<p lang="en-US"><span style="font-size: small;">This is a free version of our standard website terms and conditions document. It is identical to that document, save that this version includes an SEQ legal credit. In addition to the provisions that would typically be included in any set of website terms and conditions, this document includes provisions covering user accounts and user-generated content (although the latter are not as detailed as in some of our more sophisticated website terms and conditions documents). If your website does not feature user accounts or interactive features, you may wish to consider our website disclaimer document instead of these terms and conditions.</span></p>
<p class="western" lang="en-US"><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Section 1: Introduction</strong></span></p>
<p class="western" lang="en-US"><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Section 1.2</strong></span></p>
